com.wizturn.sdk.peripheral

Class MultiplePropertyChangeBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wizturn.sdk.peripheral.MultiplePropertyChangeBuilder

  • public class MultiplePropertyChangeBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides a way of changing multiple properties(txPower, UUID, major id and so on) of a peripheral in a single method, commit(boolean).
    Author:
    jayjay
